Package org.xchain.framework.javascript

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMergeStrategy
    Interface for defining the mechanism by which the content of a given set of URLs is to be merged.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicMergeStrategy
    Port of Chris's original code from org.xchain.namespaces.javascript.MergeJavascript for merging multiple JavaScript files together.
    CacheMergeStrategy
    Decorator IMergeStrategy which caches the result of performing a merge based on the current catalog.
    CompressJavaScriptMergeStrategy
    Merge strategy for compresses one or more Java Script documents as well as merges them.
    JsCompressor
    This class is essentially a reimplementation of org.dojotoolkit.shrinksafe.Main for using org.dojotoolkit.shrinksafe.Compressor.
    MergeUtil
